<i>Ya. Ayo lempar dia ke laut.</i>

377
00:28:02,839 --> 00:28:03,839
<i>Kamu ingat?</i>

378
00:28:03,940 --> 00:28:06,279
<i>Kim Hak Bum, Seo Joon Hee, Kang In Ho, dan Oh Tae Suk.</i>

379
00:28:06,279 --> 00:28:07,779
<i>Mereka bukan teman-temanku.</i>

380
00:28:07,940 --> 00:28:09,079
<i>Tolong beri tahu aku</i>

